name: Tribal Leaf FolkArt Mini-Napkin
description:
The Tribal Leaf ArtFolk Mini-Napkin is the first project from Penthesilea Studio! Perfect for spring and summer picnics these Tribal Leaf FolkArt Mini-Napkins are block printed on 100% cotton. 

Machine washable and tumble dry. Approx 10 x 10 as each napkin is unique. 

In sets of two.

name: Gretchen - Creepy Doll
description:
Perfect for the Amazon who loves her dolls creepy! Gretchen is s soft body with sculpy limbs. The eyes may be painted on but they see into your soul.

Hand made and a unique creation. As more dolls are added no two will be alike!
